@using WyattSandersPortfolio.Components.ReusableComponents.Contact

<article id="Singularity">
    <div class="background-img1"></div>
    <section class="feature-wrapper">
        <img class="singularity-title-img" src="Images/FeaturedProjects/Singularity_Logo.png" />
        <div class="content1 black-background">
            <h2 class="textpadding">"The card game of total control. Every decision - and accompanying consequence - is your own."</h2>

            <p class="body-text textpadding">
                Stop waiting for the perfect draw and join me for a new type of card game with <strong>no randomness.</strong>
                </p>
            <p class="body-text textpadding">
                Play your deck in the order you decide, and pull off your favorite combos every single game.
                Dive into intense 1v1 duels, strategic team battles, chaotic free-for-alls, or thrilling cooperative and solo boss incursions.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="black-background">
        <h2 class="header-text weight-heavy textpadding">Roles and Contributions:</h2>
        <p class="subheader-text textpadding">
            <strong>Game Programmer:</strong> Designed, scripted, and tested improvements to Singularity gameplay on Tabletop Simulator using Lua.
        </p>
        <p class="subheader-text textpadding">
            <strong>Game Designer:</strong> Playtested, created, and iterated on expansions and co-op content. Assisted in polishing the core set.
        </p>
        <ul class="textpadding">
            <li>
                <p class="body-text"> Refined designs through simplification and goal-oriented evaluation.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p class="body-text">
                    Created comprehensive wireframe mock-ups to assess implementation feasibility and ensure alignment with project deadlines, strategic goals, and user requirements. 
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p class="body-text">
                    Leveraged spreadsheets and data analysis to quantitatively identify and address balance issues.
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p class="body-text">
                    Actively engaged with the player community to gather feedback on new features and updates. Incorporated player insights and usability testing into development cycles to continuously improve game quality and player satisfaction.
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p class="body-text">
                    Successfully held the first official Singularity tournament via Tabletop Simulator and garnered enthusiastic support from over 1,000 backers on Gamefound.
                </p>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="black-background">
        <div class="links textpadding">
            <a class="body-text" rel="noreferrer" target="_blank" href="https://gamefound.com/en/projects/octothorpe/singularityexe">Gamefound Page</a>
